1020
01:01:58,506 --> 01:02:00,216
(The Grim Reaper)
I'm sorry I couldn't see you off.

1021
01:02:01,217 --> 01:02:02,677
I turn around and go home.

1022
01:02:07,473 --> 01:02:09,308
[THE GRIM REAPER'S PAINFUL GROAN]

1023
