[STRAINED BREATHS]

1024
01:02:35,209 --> 01:02:36,878
Where have you gone?

1025
01:02:38,045 --> 01:02:39,130
(Chairman Yoo)
From now on

1026
01:02:40,465 --> 01:02:42,967
You must serve me

1027
01:02:43,259 --> 01:02:46,804
You should remember this day well

1028
01:02:46,888 --> 01:02:48,181
Why are you doing this?

1029
01:02:48,848 --> 01:02:49,807
Who are they?

1030
01:02:49,891 --> 01:02:51,100
(Chairman Yoo)
They have long been

1031
01:02:52,518 --> 01:02:55,855
Those who were indebted to your heart

1032
01:02:55,938 --> 01:02:56,814
(Deokhwa)
Ah

1033
01:02:58,483 --> 01:02:59,567
But grandfather

1034
01:02:59,859 --> 01:03:02,820
I heard there's a sword stuck in uncle's chest, is that true?

1035
01:03:03,029 --> 01:03:04,655
How would I know that?

1036
01:03:04,947 --> 01:03:06,157
(Chairman Yoo)
In front of you

1037
01:03:06,240 --> 01:03:09,494
You must never
show any signs of it.

1038
01:03:09,827 --> 01:03:10,745
Why?

1039
01:03:11,078 --> 01:03:13,247
[HEAVY MUSIC]

1040
01:03:13,331 --> 01:03:15,583
"Kim Sun, Wang Ye"

1041
01:03:16,918 --> 01:03:18,419
[SIGNIFICANT SOUND EFFECTS]

1042
01:03:32,225 --> 01:03:33,559
(Chairman Yoo)
That black

1043
01:03:34,644 --> 01:03:37,313
Is both the image and the cause of the lily

1044
01:03:38,856 --> 01:03:41,859
The reason for the lily's existence

1045
01:03:41,943 --> 01:03:44,195
And the clue to its disappearance

1046
01:04:07,510 --> 01:04:08,845
(Kim Shin)
My life

1047
01:04:10,847 --> 01:04:12,390
My sign, you

1048
01:04:15,560 --> 01:04:18,479
I like you

1049
01:04:20,898 --> 01:04:22,733
So, I hold onto secrets

1050
01:04:25,653 --> 01:04:27,613
I try to ask for permission from the heavens

1051
01:04:29,824 --> 01:04:31,534
For even one more day without knowing

1052
01:04:32,785 --> 01:04:34,871
So, for just a hundred years without knowing

1053
01:04:37,540 --> 01:04:39,166
[TENSE SOUND EFFECTS]

1054
01:04:40,877 --> 01:04:42,920
[TENSE MUSIC]

1055
01:04:50,052 --> 01:04:54,140
[FOOTSTEPS CAN BE HEARD]

1056
01:05:22,835 --> 01:05:23,878
(Three Gods)
I know?

1057
01:05:25,755 --> 01:05:27,173
I have something to tell you

1058
01:05:27,882 --> 01:05:29,133
Is it alright if I take your time?

1059
01:05:30,176 --> 01:05:31,677
Would you like to get to the point?

1060
01:05:32,887 --> 01:05:35,973
Right now, I don't really want to face any gods

1061
01:05:36,057 --> 01:05:37,892
[HEAVY MUSIC]

1062
01:05:42,229 --> 01:05:44,106
(Grim Reaper)
Something went wrong

1063
01:05:47,902 --> 01:05:48,861
Maybe

1064
01:05:50,154 --> 01:05:51,906
It seems like it's you first

1065
01:06:01,624 --> 01:06:03,459
Where have you been, anyway?

1066
01:06:05,336 --> 01:06:06,379
I was worried this would happen

1067
01:06:07,171 --> 01:06:11,258
Even if you don't say you'll come, you should at least say you'll leave

1068
01:06:12,176 --> 01:06:13,135
Tsk

1069
01:06:16,514 --> 01:06:17,890
(Grim Reaper)
What are you curious about?

1070
01:06:19,600 --> 01:06:20,518
[CLEARS THROAT]

1071
01:06:20,601 --> 01:06:22,603
(Euntak)
Ah, yes, that...

1072
01:06:25,731 --> 01:06:27,191
(Kim Shin)
I think I've mentioned it once

1073
01:06:27,274 --> 01:06:29,902
When the bride appears,
you have to prepare to leave even further away.

1074
01:06:31,320 --> 01:06:33,906
