(Samsin)
Draw the sword and return to nothingness

1087
01:07:13,320 --> 01:07:16,240
You suddenly appeared
and said I should die

1088
01:07:17,950 --> 01:07:19,660
You should at least give a reason...

1089
01:07:19,744 --> 01:07:21,328
(Samsin)
You’ve lived long enough

1090
01:07:22,288 --> 01:07:23,873
But that child hasn't

1091
01:07:24,749 --> 01:07:26,917
I was really happy when I blessed that child

1092
01:07:27,001 --> 01:07:30,087
So just make a decision now

1093
01:07:30,546 --> 01:07:32,506
[A HOLLOW LAUGH]

1094
01:07:33,966 --> 01:07:35,676
It's ironic

1095
01:07:37,303 --> 01:07:40,097
(Kim Shin)
I don’t even know what kind of decision
you want me to make.

1096
01:07:41,891 --> 01:07:44,185
When I was born as Kim Shin for the first time

1097
01:07:44,268 --> 01:07:46,145
You must have marked me

1098
01:07:47,730 --> 01:07:49,190
Am I not your child?

1099
01:07:49,273 --> 01:07:51,150
So I'm telling you

1100
01:07:51,400 --> 01:07:54,361
My child, whom I hoped would be happy
For Kim Shin

1101
01:07:55,905 --> 01:07:58,115
Because it must be what you want the most

1102
01:07:59,700 --> 01:08:00,785
What do I want?

1103
01:08:00,868 --> 01:08:02,495
(Samshin)
Don't you want that child to live?

1104
01:08:02,578 --> 01:08:06,040
If you don't return to nothing
Euntak will die

1105
01:08:06,165 --> 01:08:07,208
[A TENSE SOUND EFFECT]

1106
01:08:09,210 --> 01:08:10,294
(Euntak)
So

1107
01:08:13,339 --> 01:08:14,715
I want to die

1108
01:08:16,675 --> 01:08:18,344
