1109
01:08:19,678 --> 01:08:21,971
Are you saying that I should take out the sword?

1110
01:08:24,600 --> 01:08:26,435
[HEAVY MUSIC]

1111
01:08:27,310 --> 01:08:28,520
[TREMBLING BREATH]

1112
01:08:28,604 --> 01:08:29,563
So

1113
01:08:32,233 --> 01:08:33,776
if I take out that sword

1114
01:08:36,112 --> 01:08:38,279
the uncle dies?

1115
01:08:42,868 --> 01:08:43,868
So

1116
01:08:48,249 --> 01:08:49,542
if I take out that sword

1117
01:08:52,336 --> 01:08:54,337
the uncle disappears?

1118
01:08:55,506 --> 01:08:57,550
Completely from this world?

1119
01:09:02,555 --> 01:09:03,848
[SOBBING]

1120
01:09:05,933 --> 01:09:06,850
[STRAINED BREATH]

1121
01:09:10,479 --> 01:09:12,731
(Samshin)
He was destined to pull your sword

1122
01:09:12,814 --> 01:09:15,401
No, you made him be born with that fate

1123
01:09:18,028 --> 01:09:20,029
[MYSTERIOUS SOUND EFFECT]

1124
01:09:20,573 --> 01:09:23,826
If you can't fulfill your role as a tool,
your value of existence will disappear

1125
01:09:23,908 --> 01:09:25,618
Because there’s no reason to exist

1126
01:09:27,246 --> 01:09:28,913
(Samshin)
So if you don’t draw the sword

1127
01:09:28,997 --> 01:09:31,125
death will keep approaching that child

1128
01:09:31,375 --> 01:09:32,792
It must have happened several times already?

1129
01:09:33,419 --> 01:09:34,420
[The moneylender screams]
[Eun-tak's scream]

1130
01:09:34,502 --> 01:09:35,462
(Moneylender)
Huh? You're really going to die

1131
01:09:35,546 --> 01:09:36,462
[AN OMINOUS SOUND EFFECT]

1132
01:09:36,546 --> 01:09:37,423
Goodbye

1133
