[TRUCK HORN]

1134
01:09:44,470 --> 01:09:45,930
(Samshin)
That's right, those accidents

1135
01:09:46,807 --> 01:09:48,142
There will be more from now on.

1136
01:09:49,143 --> 01:09:52,645
