the accidents that have happened so far.

1137
01:09:53,647 --> 01:09:56,025
You almost killed me once.

1138
01:09:56,400 --> 01:09:57,860
With your own hands

1139
01:09:59,486 --> 01:10:00,404
Move.

1140
01:10:00,487 --> 01:10:01,322
