After living for a hundred years, one day

1145
01:10:22,092 --> 01:10:23,969
On a day that felt just right

1146
01:10:26,430 --> 01:10:27,806
It was my first love

1147
01:10:30,059 --> 01:10:31,393
Wishing to confess

